@startuml
[Diagnostic Console] as Console

note top of Console: Captures operator intent

note bottom of Console
  Stores triage decisions
  beside each session
end note

note left of Console
  Receives playback markers
  from archived runs
end note

note right of Console: Publishes review status
@enduml
